\u00fcrgen Kohler]]\n| DF\n| 105\n| 2\n| style=\"text-align:left\" | 24 September 1986\n| style=\"text-align:left\" | {{fb|DEN}}\n| style=\"text-align:left\" | 4 July 1998\n| style=\"text-align:left\" | {{fb|CRO}}\n| <ref>{{DFB|40679|J\u00fcrgen Kohler|type=player}}</ref>\n|-\n| data-sort-value=\"Mertesacker, Per\" | [[Per Mertesacker]]\n| DF\n| 104\n| 4\n| style=\"text-align:left\" | 9 October 2004\n| style=\"text-align:left\" | {{fb|IRN}}\n| style=\"text-align:left\" | 13 July 2014\n| style=\"text-align:left\" | {{fb|ARG}}\n| <ref>{{DFB|7500|Per Mertesacker|type=player}}</ref>\n|-\n| data-sort-value=\"Beckenbauer, Franz\" | [[Franz Beckenbauer]]\n| DF\n| 103\n| 14\n| style=\"text-align:left\" | 26 September 1965\n| style=\"text-align:left\" | {{fb|SWE}}\n| style=\"text-align:left\" | 23 February 1977\n| style=\"text-align:left\" | {{fb|FRA}}\n| <ref>{{DFB|41477|Franz Beckenbauer|type=player}}</ref>\n|-\n| data-sort-value=\"Hassler, Thomas\" | [[Thomas H\u00e4\u00dfler]]\n| MF\n| 101\n| 11\n| style=\"text-align:left\" | 31 August 1988\n| style=\"text-align:left\" | {{fb|FIN}}\n| style=\"text-align:left\" | 20 June 2000\n| style=\"text-align:left\" | {{fb|POR}}\n| <ref>{{DFB|40777|Thomas H\u00e4\u00dfler|type=player}}</ref>\n|-\n| data-sort-value=\"Muller, Thomas\" style=\"background:#FBEC5D\" | [[Thomas M\u00fcller]] *\n| FW\n| 100\n| 38\n| style=\"text-align:left\" | 3 March 2010\n| style=\"text-align:left\" | {{fb|ARG}}\n| style=\"text-align:left\" | 19 November 2018\n| style=\"text-align:left\" | {{fb|NED}}\n| <ref>{{DFB|3249|Thomas M\u00fcller|type=player}}</ref>\n|-\n| data-sort-value=\"Ballack, Michael\" | [[Michael Ballack]]\n| MF\n| 98\n| 42\n| style=\"text-align:left\" | 28 April 1999\n| style=\"text-align:left\" | {{fb|SCO}}\n| style=\"text-align:left\" | 3 March 2010\n| style=\"text-align:left\" | {{fb|ARG}}\n| <ref>{{DFB|5668|Michael Ballack|type=player}}</ref>\n|-\n| data-sort-value=\"Kroos, Toni\" style=\"background:#FBEC5D\" | [[Toni Kroos]] *\n| MF\